sentences.english: It tries to shoo the finches away, but a gruesome kind of artistry comes into play here.
sentences.chinese: 它試圖決定離開，但是加拉的可怕的藝術性進場。

sentences.english: Ryan snuck into the movie after it started.
sentences.chinese: 雷恩在電影開演後偷溜進場。

sentences.english: Come over here and get ready to go in.
sentences.chinese: 請你們出來，到集合地點，準備進場。

sentences.english: The fee for the admittance of commodities to shopping malls is even higher than that for supermarkets.
sentences.chinese: 相比較超市，百貨商場的進場費還要高。

sentences.english: What is that like to see Yao carry the flag.
sentences.chinese: 你看到姚明在開幕式舉旗進場時感覺怎樣？

sentences.english: Woolly Razorback comes into play with three ice counters on it.
sentences.chinese: 粗茸刃背豬進場時上面有三個寒冰指示物。

sentences.english: When Grave Defiler comes into play, reveal the top four cards of your library.
sentences.chinese: 當墓場污者進場時，展示你牌庫頂上的四張牌。

sentences.english: When Mind Maggots comes into play, choose and discard any number of creature cards.
sentences.chinese: 當心靈蛆進場時，選擇棄掉任意數量的生物牌。

sentences.english: Reporters wishing to attend the conference in-person must have a valid press credential for access.
sentences.chinese: 想要到現場報道的記者必須有一個有效記者證來進場。

sentences.english: He watched as the brothers completed their entrance and positioned themselves before polished oak pews.
sentences.chinese: 他看着武士們全部進場安坐在擦亮的橡木長凳上。

sentences.english: When Booby Trap comes into play, name a card other than a basic land.
sentences.chinese: 當詭雷進場時，說出一張基本地之外的牌名稱。

sentences.english: When Roc Hatchling comes into play, put four shell counters on it.
sentences.chinese: 當雛巨鳥進場時，放四個蛋殼指示物在上面。

sentences.english: Search your library for an artifact card and put that artifact into play. Shuffle your library afterward.
sentences.chinese: 從你的牌庫中搜尋任一張神器牌，並將其放置進場。

sentences.english: At the beginning of a ceremonial parade,he gives the order to march on.
sentences.chinese: 閱兵儀式開始時，他下令部隊進場。

sentences.english: Organize constructors to enter the field and build infrastructures before construction according to the plan.
sentences.chinese: 按計劃組織施工人員進場，搞好臨建設施。
